ro"},{"id":1077370,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","description":"假期去农村<br />吃饭时听上一辈的酒后聊天<br />一边对延迟退休深恶痛绝<br />一边又说希望 ID 上的年纪改小点 好找工作","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1077370","replies":28,"created_ts":1727832928,"created":"09:35:28","title":"哎 魔幻现实","author":"nightnotlate","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/nightnotlate","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0bb6/d4a5/589794_mini.png?m=1660731939"},{"id":1077376,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1695370146","description":"<p>一人只能说一句</p>\n<p>我先来:</p>\n<p>「我对面的同事喜欢穿拖鞋上班,夏天脚特别臭,我多次想吐🤮」</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1077376","replies":25,"created_ts":1727838951,"created":"11:15:51","title":"[2024 吐槽大会]说说隔壁工位同事最让你讨厌的行为","author":"jiaoguan1688","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/jiaoguan1688","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e043/056c/456168_mini.png?m=1577366669"},{"id":1077429,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>我爸最近突发奇想，跟着一个在深圳卖家电的远亲突然间有了联系，打算一起去南非卖电器，正在办签证。</p>\n<p>感觉非常不靠谱，但是我对此又完全不懂不知道怎么反驳，家里人对他的态度只能说。。。不好说。有没有懂哥教一下具体什么个情况？</p>\n<p>关于我爸：70 后，一句英语不会，初中辍学。一分钱积蓄没有，每天下班后的爱好就是看抖音战狼视频。</p>\n<p>关于那个亲戚：共享同一个曾祖父，一般四五年才一起吃一顿饭的那种。早年在福建当倒爷，现在在深圳做电器批发。</p>\n<p>其它因素：我爸受到延迟退休影响，一下子延迟了三年，但是据传明年公司就会把他们部门裁撤掉。估计也是因此才打算搞事情。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1077429","replies":22,"created_ts":1727869324,"created":"19:42:04","title":"一句英语不会，去南非卖电器是个好选择吗？","author":"kandaakihito","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/kandaakihito","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b8a8/c05f/478739_mini.png?m=1726622705"},{"id":1077373,"node":"音乐","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/music","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a87f/f679/4_mini.png?m=1625264761","description":"<p>真的是日本漫画式美人 下午打算窝在家看看她的电视剧\n听完她的歌感觉那个年代的歌特别好听 有 80 后出来推荐几首歌吗？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1077373","replies":21,"created_ts":1727835685,"created":"10:21:25","title":"刚刚看了周慧敏《自作多情》LIVE 1993 好美","author":"Michae1Jacks0n","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Michae1Jacks0n","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/43a6/3ad7/630464_mini.png?m=1721313723"},{"id":1077459,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>这几年苹果手机实在是不怎么行，对我来说，耳机是切换到安卓时唯一 block 的点了</p>\n<p>几年前找了一圈，可惜没找到同等级别的</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1077459","replies":18,"created_ts":1727882841,"created":"23:27:21","title":"考虑从 ios 切换到安卓了；耳机是唯一 block，从降噪和通透模式等影响日常体验的方面综合来看，现在安卓生态有 airpods pro 2 这种级别的耳机吗？","author":"ddddd0","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ddddd0","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/028f/4c82/363906_mini.png?m=1722059430"},{"id":1077436,"node":"Android","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/android","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1651385965","description":"我在商场里看了几家体验店，小米 vivoOPPO 三星，只有 vivo 的热点共享里不包含以太网网络共享这个功能，其他几家都有，无论是低端机还是旗舰机。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1077436","replies":18,"created_ts":1727874304,"created":"21:05:04","title":"为啥 vivo iqoo 的 Origin os 把以太网网络共享这个功能删掉了","author":"CNM47589","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/CNM47589","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1e365ff99b8451c50bdebadbea9f2aef?s=24&d=retro"}]